flowchart LR
    MSG[your new message] --> SCORE["score = 0.65·lexical + 0.35·(confidence × decay)"]
    DECAY[recency decay<br/>~60-day half-life] --> SCORE
    SCORE --> TH{above relevance bar?}
    TH -->|yes| INJ[inject — capped at ~2000 tokens]
    TH -->|no| HOLD[stay out of the prompt]
    RULES[active behavior rules] --> INJ
